Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,brume0425僅分享於伊莉論壇/動畫下載區(免空)請勿任意轉載
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.75,0:00:17.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:20.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,天亮囉 該起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:23.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再讓我睡五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:25.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:29.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再等我體溫上升五度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:33.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,話說米亞 妳為什麼會在我床上?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:37.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為太冷了體溫升不上去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:39.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,想讓Darling幫我暖身體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:42.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,拉米亞族是變溫動物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:44.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那我去準備熱水澡妳等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:45.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:50.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我想讓Darling親自幫我暖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:56.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling的體溫傳過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:00:58.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,胸部!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:00.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,冷靜‧‧‧我要冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:02.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不能有邪念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:04.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧等‧‧‧脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:06.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,靜動脈完全被勒住了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等一下米亞  這樣會缺氧的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:09.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,棄權 棄權
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:12.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling 別那麼粗暴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:13.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,又睡了!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:16.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不想個辦法掙脫的話‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.96,0:01:22.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不‧‧‧不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:26.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,一放鬆反而更緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:27.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不妙!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:29.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:36.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Da‧‧‧Darling 尾巴的尖端有點‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:38.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,發現弱點?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,效果拔群啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:45.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,纏得漸漸鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:48.53,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling! 在這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:48.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是脖子還是緊緊的纏著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:50.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不妙啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:51.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,意識快要‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:53.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:56.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快點鬆開我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:02.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要那麼用力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:05.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,還以為要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:10.69,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,已經‧‧‧不行了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:12.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:13.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:17.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,去了!  !  !
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:30.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的 我知道了 這就起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,都怪Darling一大早就這麼激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:35.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:38.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再等我五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:03:03.26,標題,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}「拉米亞的同居日常」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:15.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,趁米亞還沒睡第三次 得讓她暖暖身體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:20.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,為了讓米亞寄宿房子改造了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:23.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,到處都太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:26.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,廁所?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:28.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她是怎麼上廁所的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,熱水準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 剛準備 {\fnArial Unicode MS}‧ ‧ ‧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,謝謝 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:43.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼我先下去泡囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:47.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊 ~真暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,日本的浴池真是好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:55.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我在書上看過 日本好像有叫溫泉這東西的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好想和Darling一起去一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:59.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這個‧‧‧那個‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:03.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的 你在偷瞄什麼啊呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:03.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真色~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:07.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那我去準備做早餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:09.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:13.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,有熱水了就不需要我來暖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:19.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且 我還知道 溫泉裡有個叫混浴的文化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:18.26,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧ 米亞‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以說Darling也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:21.73,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,背‧‧‧背後‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:25.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞從禁止事項來說這樣不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:28.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,混浴是很不好的東西嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:31.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,溫泉裡還有那麼見不得人的文化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不‧‧‧不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:35.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那讓我體驗一下混浴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也是為了文化交流才來日本的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.23,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,等, 等, 等!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:43.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我才不想和Darling以外的人混浴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我初體驗的對象‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊~好冷! 我的體溫要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling 你在做什麼啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:06:00.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,本設施不提供混浴的服務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.00,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,關起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:03.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是無情啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,超人氣組合 ANM48
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.08,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&H360AF5&\3c&HFF00FF&\pos(510,542)}獸 耳 相 伴 每 一 天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:19.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,出道以來連續更新榜首的紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:20.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你覺得怎麼樣呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:23.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,作為世界上首支已亞人種組成的偶像團體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:25.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,震撼力非同小可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:29.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不止是震撼力 還有非常可愛的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:37.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,ANM48能如此活耀 多虧了三年前實施的法案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:40.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,他種族間交流法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:47.92,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(1060,170)\fs40\c&H5253EB&\3c&HFFFFFF&}他種族間交流法實施三週年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:44.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是為了長期被政府隱藏起來的非人類種族
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:47.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,進行交流而制定的法案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:52.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因此 文化交流正積極推進了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:56.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所幸沒有發生重大摩擦 他們也漸漸融入人類社會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:00.35,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,不過 世界沒有想像那樣發生了巨大變化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.66,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,是啊 我前幾天還遇到了某個‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,才沒有那種事‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:05.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,一大早我就很不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:14.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,幾天前我根本還沒想過事情會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,早安 來留主公人君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:25.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎麼了 竟然嚇成這樣 把我忘了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:29.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我是他種族間交流的協調員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:30.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:32.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:34.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,為什麼隨意的進來我家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:36.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,能也給我一份早餐嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳是來吃飯的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:39.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,還有‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:43.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,來確認你是否違反了禁止事項
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:49.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,為了文化交流而來的亞人種要是傷害他們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:47.42,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(374,558)}拉米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:48.34,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(364,562)}勇 者 攻 擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:49.23,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(402,564)}拉米亞受到58點傷害!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:53.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,會依據他種族交流法受到懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:50.26,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\fs56\pos(444,272)}打 敗 了 拉 米 亞 !
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:51.51,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\fs56\pos(544,514)}獲 得 了           4649 經 驗 值 !
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:58.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,作為寄宿家庭方 怕你對法案無知所以才來確認的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:07:59.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什麼無知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:03.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,本來就是墨須小姐搞錯了才把米亞帶來我家的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我家又不是寄宿家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:07.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒有這段記憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:09.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:10.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,太隨意了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳這也能算他種族間交流協調員嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:13.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這個先放一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:14.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,居然就放一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:20.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然米亞說這裡好 那你就需要好好學習才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:23.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你父母在國外工作真是剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎麼單方面地‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再來杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:27.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好~好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我才沒傷害她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:35.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,也有那方面含意的傷害喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那種事情‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:41.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她也有正常的生殖器 要做的話也能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒有被緊逼過嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:45.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,畢竟她們可是很熱情的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:51.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,代表種族而來的女孩子的純潔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:54.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,人類要是玷汙她 就變成外交問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:58.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果你要是越過了那條線的話‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:02.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就會依法將你逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:06.55,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:06.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她則會被遣返回國
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:10.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,雖然很可憐 但這就是規定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:13.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼 Sex了沒?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:15.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎 沒有‧‧‧絕對沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:19.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是有稍微考慮過吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:22.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她下半身雖然是蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是身材火辣  胸部也很大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:27.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且又是個美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:29.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,最重要的是十分迷戀你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:31.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再加上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:34.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你很容易屈服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:35.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂! 妳在幹什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:44.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果對Darling出手 就算是墨須小姐也不能原諒!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:46.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,看來他也很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳有在聽嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:50.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哦~開個玩笑 玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且我這就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:58.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling君 請務必切記不要觸犯禁止事項喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:09:59.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個  米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:11.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳不把身體擦乾的話身體又會冷了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:15.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個禁止事項就那麼重要嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:15.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:20.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個時候‧‧‧我第一次來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:23.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為我們拉米亞族下半身是蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:26.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,第一次見到的人一般肯定會感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:30.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以我很不安你是否會接受我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:49.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是Darling你用笑容迎接了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:54.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這讓我非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:59.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,最近的電視上也經常看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:01.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以沒有那麼害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:07.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,和禁止事項沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:11.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只要是Darling對我做什麼也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:13.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,讓我受傷我也可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:16.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧米亞? 等‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:18.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:24.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,留下無法磨滅的第一次痕跡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為我‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:30.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,最喜歡Darling了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:36.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:37.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:39.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,禁止事項有那麼重要嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是那回事‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:45.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我就快要‧‧‧斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:51.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,斷了! ! !
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:53.63,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling! ! ! !
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:57.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,對不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:12:00.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling 對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:00.24,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.59,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:03.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只不過是肩膀脫臼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真的是讓你受苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:14.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling 對不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:19.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}魔物娘!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:25.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,約會  約會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,今天要和Darling約會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,約會!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:31.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼關於約會—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:35.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,對社會見習的最後確認
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:39.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,寄宿家庭不能讓留學生單獨行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:43.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,必須整天共同行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:45.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好好帶她再街上逛逛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:50.69,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我說墨須小姐 這不是協調員的工作嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:53.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也是有很多事要忙的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:58.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,絕對不能帶去愛情旅館喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快走吧! Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:04.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,約會開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:33.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,印象中日本是很死板的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:35.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但沒想到有那麼多好玩的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:38.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不過到處都是人類專用的設施太狹小了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:40.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,有點讓人遺憾的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好想去唱卡拉OK呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:45.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,卡拉OK的包廂太狹窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:49.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,現在社會整體還沒做到對應全種族
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:50.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒辦法‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:55.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快看快看Darling 這間店對應全種族喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:56.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,進去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:59.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧別拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:04.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這是‧‧‧內衣店?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:05.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那‧‧‧我在外面等‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:06.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:10.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須小姐不是說過要一直一起行動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:14.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不好意思 有拉米亞用的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在這邊 請慢慢挑選
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:16.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,感覺好不自在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:22.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,話說米亞有穿內褲嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是怎麼穿的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:27.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling 你覺得哪一件適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:31.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我不怎麼穿胸罩 所以不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:35.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是 我也不太懂胸罩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:36.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳試穿一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,試穿?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.69,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧等 為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:45.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為我們不管什麼時候都要在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:47.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我直接穿給你看你選一件喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:54.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我想穿Darling喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:57.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,想讓Darling能更加喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以要仔細看好在選哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:01.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哪‧‧‧哪件都很合適喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:04.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,全部都買了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:03.61,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:07.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這是什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:10.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,矽膠隱形胸貼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:12.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不過這形狀也夠奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:15.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,背面是貼合的還有點熱呼呼的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:17.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Da‧‧‧Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:23.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個‧‧‧強行把你拉進試衣間是我不好 我道歉‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:25.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以把內褲還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:26.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:28.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的! Darling你這個變態
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:34.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,原來有穿啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:35.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:42.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling真是的 玩弄內褲只有變態才會做的事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:46.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不 那是我不知道 我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:51.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不過那麼在意的話乾脆給你看吧Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,都說了‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:54.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哇! 那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:57.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是噁心 居然叫Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真噁心呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:06.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling !?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:09.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,剛剛你是故意擋住?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:12.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞 想想禁止事項
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:16.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,人類不能傷害他種族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是反過來也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:23.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果傷害人類的話 就會被遣返回國了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,他種族居然還有這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:30.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我是第一次看見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.55,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,現拉米亞族NOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那男的是誰 男朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:35.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那‧‧‧那個 等等‧‧‧各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:38.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請不要隨意拍照好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:42.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling 我想去沒人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不引人注目的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:50.27,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,愛情旅館!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:52.00,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,跑哪裡去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.70,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,好像是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:00.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我要冷靜‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:03.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這是緊急避難絕沒有下流的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:08.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這裡的浴室雖然比不上Darling家的但也很大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:11.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米‧‧‧米亞 妳沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:13.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯~稍微好些了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不過這裡是HOTEL吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:18.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我並沒有做過夜的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只是休息而已 不過夜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:22.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,明明是HOTEL卻不過夜?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那這裡是做什麼的地方啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:26.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是做什麼的呢‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,話說這個是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快把那個放一邊去!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:39.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,果然人類還是會抗拒我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:46.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,對我們溫柔的人也是受法律要求才會那樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:51.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling這麼溫柔對待我也是因為怕被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:53.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒‧‧‧沒那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:57.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,看 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:03.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我並不可怕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:06.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這樣的無防備
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:10.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就算Darling傷害我 我也不會反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:14.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,即使這樣Darling還會害怕我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:16.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:26.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不許動!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我們是他種族間交流法保安局的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:32.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我們得到情報有人帶拉米亞族少女做出淫亂行為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:36.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我以觸犯他種族間交流法名義將對你進行‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:39.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊啦 Darling君!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:40.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:42.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳為什麼會在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:47.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀啦 可別小看國家權力機關的情報收集能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:50.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嘛 說白了就是Twitter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:01.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:04.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,剛才的蛇女居然來愛情旅館了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:06.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真的是好噁心!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:08.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等一下 你們這些人!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.47,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎麼那傢伙能做嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:12.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,話說回來她有OO嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:14.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,別笑死人了 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:17.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:38.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,下手太重‧‧‧了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:44.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好痛! 痛痛痛‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:47.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你是男孩子吧 忍耐一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不就是稍微傷到關節而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:50.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:53.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個 對方?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:57.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我跟那兩個人很和氣地談了一下後他們就和解了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:01.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,還有 以防萬一確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:02.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你臉上的傷是‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:03.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我摔倒傷到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:08.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼 多多保重喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:16.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:19.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,為什麼要那麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:23.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個尾擊是我自己撞上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:25.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不算什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:29.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是‧‧‧我不是說那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:32.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你想想 我出手的話就是普通打架而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:37.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要是妳打了那種傢伙被遣返回國就太不值了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:43.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在作為拉米亞族或其他種族前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:46.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞只是一個女孩子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:50.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我只是不能原諒那兩個人對女孩子那麼過分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:52.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真的只有這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:56.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling ! !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,果然還是會變成這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:01.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:06.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling是真心把我當作一名女孩子看待的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:09.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那剛才的事‧‧‧繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:10.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:13.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧好不容易躲過被遣返回國的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:16.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒關係 這下初體驗的隔閡也能消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:19.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,話說回來Darling君 今天的晚餐是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:22.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳‧‧‧妳在幹什麼啊 墨須小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:24.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,幹什麼!? 我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:26.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,太自說自話了‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:30.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊‧‧‧讓他們和解真的太累了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:31.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,區區咖哩不嫌棄的話請用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:34.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀啦 真的 怎感覺不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,難得氣氛這麼好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:41.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞 妳忘了這個喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:47.24,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎啊! 啊------------! ! !
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:21.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\c&HA0CCF9&}妳是?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:24.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H781777&\c&HA0CCF9&}帕皮! 帕皮是哈耳庇的帕皮喲!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:26.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H781777&\c&HA0CCF9&}哎? 帕皮哈皮帕皮?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:28.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H781777&\c&HA0CCF9&}是哈庇厄族的帕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:31.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H781777&\c&HA0CCF9&}不對‧‧‧ 是帕比的帕皮?
