Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:44.22,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,Monster  Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:47.87,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,MonMonMonMon  Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:51.39,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,Monster Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:57.21,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,MonMonMon  Monster’S life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:06.51,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其一 不要在意他人目光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:09.07,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,要膽大心細 慎重選擇目標
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:11.61,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其二 日常問候要適度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:15.09,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,做好心理準備就上陣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:18.85,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其三 發現機會要迅速瞄準
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:20.48,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,開火開火開火開火!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.97,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其四 不需要手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:25.85,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,最後只需給目標的心致命一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:30.56,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,只有有愛 一分就足夠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:36.78,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,比這更重要的是 遵循慾望的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:39.79,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,衝啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:42.40,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,嘿 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:45.21,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為有你就是最強 對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.84,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,能一直和你在一起就是最棒 不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:50.37,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,無論前方會遇到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:53.17,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,和你一起就ALL OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:55.74,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,如今以無庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:58.48,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,這肯定就是宇宙第一的LOVE 對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:02.86,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,等不及你的答案 我已經
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:07.73,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,以最高速 Fall in Love!
